Description
===========

xkcd is a simple command-line XKCD tool. It allows you to search, download or
read the transcript of a XKCD.

Documentation
=============

Usage: xkcd.py [-d] XKCD

Options:
    -d, --download  Download corresponding xkcd and do not print anything.

Argument:
    XKCD    If it is a number, prints the title and the transcript of the
            corresponding xkcd.
            Otherwise, performs a research to find the corresponding xkcds.

Dependencies
============

docopt  https://github.com/docopt/docopt or "pip install docopt"

